item.name: Upload a new block to blockchain

body.raw:
--- !Hash
Digest: '0000000097259cdbbf6438494ab23634119727008c74972da217419ae9062c0617e20495b4c2f8081da2369dc43d9ade'
--- !Block
Timestamp: 2018-09-15T21:04:06.758144Z
Difficulty: 20
Nonce: 39665226
Miner: TeskaLabs
Transactions:
  - !Transaction
    Id: 1
    Fee: 1.0

request.description:
Upload a new block to a CoinGame server.
The server will validate the block and if the block is valid, it will be added to a blockchain.
You must provide a previous hash and a current (new) block as a text, the server will calculate the hash of the block to verify a difficulty.
